<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.9.3">
<l>uṇṭula kēḻiṉai yumoru pālaka ṉālilaimēl</l>
<l>kaṇṭuyil koṇṭukan takaru māṇikka  māmalaiyai</l>
<l>tiṇṭiṟal mākari cērtiru māliruñ cōlainiṉṟa</l>
<l>vaṇṭartam kōviṉai yiṉṟaṇu kuṅkole ṉāyiḻaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Will my jewel of the herders now be near the king of celestials</l>
<l>Who stands in Tirumāliruñcōlai with strong, vigorous, great elephants,</l>
<l>That great, dark emerald mountain who was content [as] a child</l>
<l>Sleeping on a banyan leaf, having eaten the seven worlds?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
